data.description: THIS PRICE IMPROVEMENT IS THE REAL DEAL!! MOTIVATED SELLER - ALL REASONABLE OFFERS WILL BE CONSIDERED. Large home in established community in McLeansville, with easy access to the 840 loop, allowing for a quick drive to anywhere in the Triad - east or west! 4 bedrooms and 3 FULL bathrooms, first floor flex room with accessibility to one of the full baths, large family room with gas log fireplace, and big kitchen with comfortable eat-in dining area. The layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating ideal space for entertaining for small and large get togethers! Primary bedroom is a true retreat, offering plenty of room for oversized furniture, great closet space, and roomy ensuite. The other bedrooms are nicely sized w/ great closets. Sit back and unwind in your fenced-in backyard, perfect for enjoying fun or relaxation! Home sits nicely towards back of cul-de-sac for add'l quiet and privacy.
